skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
Overcoming challenges holding you back from improving your lifestyle and quality of life is possible with the #challengeyourlimitations training program.

Based on the NLP Training (neuro linguistic programming) I received and used to get tremendous improvements in improving my healthy lifestyle after experiencing major heart problems, I can see how overcoming challenges in our lives makes all the difference in your quality of life.

This Flash briefing will give you regular weekly tips on motivation and decision making life skills you can use immediately to improve your life.

Break though limitations holding you back from your best life.

Don’t be a “Lone Ranger” and reach out for the coaching and mentorship to help you succeed even more. You can also join our private and supportive community to help you during challenging times.
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
